parts.text:
Magpie

```json
{
  "application": "Magpie",
  "details": {
    "description": "Scripts for running Hadoop on traditional HPC systems.",
    "software": [
      "Hadoop",
      "HDFS",
      "HBase",
      "Tensorflow",
      "Horovod",
      "MPI",
      "SLURM"
    ],
    "resource_requirements": {
      "nodes": "<my_node_count>",
      "time": "<my_time_in_minutes>",
      "partition": "<my_partition>",
      "job_name": "<my_job_name>",
      "local_scratch": "/tmp/${USER}/magpie"
    },
    "configurations": {
      "MAGPIE_SCRIPTS_HOME": "${HOME}/magpie",
      "MAGPIE_JOB_TYPE": "tensorflow-horovod",
      "MAGPIE_STARTUP_TIME": "30",
      "MAGPIE_SHUTDOWN_TIME": "30",
      "MAGPIE_ONE_TIME_RUN": "yes",
      "MAGPIE_PYTHON": "/usr/bin/python",
      "TENSORFLOW_HOROVOD_SETUP": "yes",
      "TENSORFLOW_HOROVOD_LOCAL_DIR": "/tmp/${USER}/tensorflow-horovod",
      "TENSORFLOW_HOROVOD_JOB": "synthetic-benchmark",
      "TENSORFLOW_HOROVOD_SCRIPT_PATH": "/path/to/executable"
    }
  }
}
```
